# DD-3: Infrastructure Validation
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All infrastructure changes via IaC

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- IaC: Infrastructure as Code, automating provisioning and configuration.

ENFORCE: All IaC scripts must be validated for correctness and idempotence before application; all changes must be logged.
PROHIBIT: Manual unverified infrastructure changes; scripts with destructive side effects.
ON VIOLATION: Abort infrastructure deployment → notify Orchestrator and DevOps Lead.
